s trajectory 37 38 39 40 39 41 42 43 44 Gestational diabetes mellitus (GDM) is a common complication developed during pregnancy that can benefit from biometric-based wearable technologies. GDM affects ~14% of pregnant women worldwide and leads to 10 \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
